{"tid":1699520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚十八區悼念活動","createTime":"2019-11-08T05:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T06:13:34.000Z","uid":222809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae783fe211074f0ee019effb106e164cdb52b6c","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"8/11/2019<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">5:00PM 觀塘 聯校集會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">8:00PM 尚德停車場 周同學悼念活動<br />\n8:00PM 十八區遍地開花</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">8:00PM 旺角北 夢遊大講堂<br />\n8:00PM 大角咀 逆權司機放映會<br />\n8:00PM 大白田西 社區論壇<br />\n9:00PM 離島人集氣 音樂分享會<br />\n9:00PM 火炭 和你跑<br />\n9:00PM 香港仔 和你跑</span><br />\n<br />\n今晚8點尚德停車場需要大量街坊 和理非<br />\n其他人8點自己個區見（揀八點係因為需要時間比手足準備 雖然我都明白一定有mon po狗 但個人認為現時要號召大量人力有難度）<br />\n<br />\n集合點跟之前<br />\n地點：第一集合點／第二集合點／第三集合點<br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城／<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場／<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙廣場／鳳德公園／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場／<br />\n土瓜灣何田文九龍城：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場／<br />\n紅磡黃埔：聚寶坊<br />\n將軍澳：Popcorn/新都城（自選）／香港單車公園／<br />\n沙田：新城市廣場／車公廟站 曾大屋遊樂場<br />\n馬鞍山：新港城／鞍誠街花園／<br />\n大埔：大埔超級城／大埔中央廣場／<br />\n上水： 上水廣場／彩園廣場<br />\n屯門：屯門市廣場／屯門政府合署／新和里球場<br />\n天水圍：嘉湖銀座／天耀<br />\n元朗：Yoho／大馬路<br />\n銅鑼灣：紀利佐治街／東角道<br />\n太古：太古城中心／鰂魚涌公園／<br />\n柴小杏：柴灣橋／柴灣公園<br />\n西區：西寶城／<br />\n南區：香港仔中心／<br />\n東涌：東薈城噴水池／富東商場<br />\n所有人開花前搵商場行街 以策安全<br />\n<br />\n現時係遮打手足注意安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 今晚其他與周同學無關嘅主題活動都希望可以取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 講句 對唔住 上一個po標題開得唔好 引黎部分人不滿 對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周同學一路好走 黑警不得善終 香港人還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c92213675971ead825f2a9da4cb80776d6c7453","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"3f07de6c7e90992c8e5783010278e890390b284f","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"5603b61e8c68a9eb91fcf9cea28df3dfc0b4fb42","tid":1699520,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"你個「集合點跟之前」嗰張list係早兩日藍絲group亂鳩咁傳嗰個fake list"},{"pid":"b8f7af8432740cedc6352a7e93861f283837f8e6","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"4b41798c0da39746d76a60a2c713d23e7dc84d5e","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5603b61e8c68a9eb91fcf9cea28df3dfc0b4fb42","tid":1699520,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"你個「集合點跟之前」嗰張list係早兩日藍絲group亂鳩咁傳嗰個fake list"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"認真？ 有冇新嘅list"},{"pid":"49e8940bf5057f2fd0c7db28f3524bda242d91cb","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5603b61e8c68a9eb91fcf9cea28df3dfc0b4fb42","tid":1699520,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"你個「集合點跟之前」嗰張list係早兩日藍絲group亂鳩咁傳嗰個fake list"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRLNqmW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRLNqmW.jpg&h=6e056db4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThis One？"},{"pid":"1e71fbcc9d98ebfa937b131ed5fe1b3e50737d6c","tid":1699520,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e8940bf5057f2fd0c7db28f3524bda242d91cb","tid":1699520,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5603b61e8c68a9eb91fcf9cea28df3dfc0b4fb42","tid":1699520,"uid":168267,